-02-19T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我自己揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就係唔想幾皮野買左我唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有咩好揀 都係大大細一粒 又唔會要有碎石個d架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我最後揀左隻最簡單既款 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係燈光下睇粒石係有分別<br />\n<br />\n其實求婚果陣就算粒石好多瑕疵都唔會唔鍾意架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bf2eac6f8e6dbb6dab8b0a1d30aca298a8f153","tid":126651,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我自己揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就係唔想幾皮野買左我唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有咩好揀 都係大大細一粒 又唔會要有碎石個d架啦</blockquote><br />\n其實你唔係用射燈射撚住根本肉眼分唔到咩色水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寧願大粒D好過色水好，當然唔係叫你揀最差嘅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7165cb89090392821c9804058048f85da92945db","tid":126651,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"求婚戒指同結婚戒指好似唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff969e7e69bfb1dc80e7192cfddbcb3db8b8f8ec","tid":126651,"uid":72557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求婚戒指同結婚戒指好似唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似唔同，留俾紫青爸答你"},{"pid":"bd0479c8c1a23810c5bbe6a1db94053ad4c38f90","tid":126651,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係自己去揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  完全無驚喜</blockquote><br />\n係囉<img sr